org.springframework.actuate.metrics
Class Metric

java.lang.Object
  org.springframework.actuate.metrics.Metric

public final class Metric
extends Object

Immutable class that can be used to hold any arbitrary system measurement value. For example a metric might record the number of active connections.

Author:
Dave Syer
See Also:
MetricRepository, CounterService
